org.eclipse.smarthome.core.thing

Class Channel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.smarthome.core.thing.Channel

  • @NonNullByDefault
public class Channel
extends Object
    Channel is a part of a Thing that represents a functionality of it. Therefore Items can be linked a to a channel. The channel only accepts a specific item type which is specified by getAcceptedItemType() methods.
    Author:
    Dennis Nobel - Initial contribution, Alex Tugarev - Extended about default tags, Benedikt Niehues - fix for Bug https://bugs.eclipse.org/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=445137 considering default values, Chris Jackson - Added properties, label, description, Kai Kreuzer - Removed linked items from channel
